---
title: Bacon Baked Beans & Roasted Potatoes with Sour Cream & Parsley
description: What's rich, smokey, cheesy and downright delicious? These flavour-packed baked beans, that's what! Add some roasted potatoes with crispy edges and a fresh green salad for a hearty dinner that the whole family will love.
